track_notes:
Track starts at a parking lot for hikers and passes Regensburger Stein with a nice view leading to Klosterstein, the summit of Vogelsang.
Distance 2.7 km, height gain 249 m, takes me 55 minutes to get up.
48.940 277 191 N, 12.926 272 233 E (Wanderparkplatz, 100 m up in the forest, close to Grün 20, 94250 Achslach, Germany

Start near Faßlehen / Oberhirschberg. Limited parking possiblities on the side of the road. Takes about 1h to summit. Follow way #6 resp. #8. 
Trailhead can also be used as start to Butzen DM/BM-019.
